views.markdown: If you need help with "Filza File Manager", you can contact TIGI Software , the developer, via e-mail.
BigBoss  is the maintainer of the package "Filza File Manager". Please contact them via email for any questions on this version of the package.
If you found a mistake in the depiction or cannot download the package, you can reach out to the maintainer of the "KT-Stations" repo, KT-Stations.
